In re Resignation of Hamann.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hamann (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1205.]

(No. 92-154 Submitted February 12, 1992 Decided February 19, 1992.)

The resignation of William A. Hamann, Jr. as an attorney, Registration No. 0033765, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
